---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageTitle from '../components/Title.astro'
import SubTitle from '../components/SubTitle.astro'

---

<Layout title="About Me", description="About Me" />

<main class="container max-w-screen-lg py-30 mx-auto text-lg">
    <div id="text-part" class="container pt-24 h-screen mx-auto">
        <PageTitle title="How can I help you ?"/>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-is-4 pt-12">
            <div class="flex align-center">
                <img
                style="border-radius: 50% 20% / 10% 40%"
                src="/images/profile.jpg"
                draggable="false"
                alt="profile-photo"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
                <SubTitle title="A brief introduction" />
                <div class="text-justify">
                With a Master's degree in Computer Science and a specialization in <strong>modeling</strong> and <strong>testing</strong>, I have gained a deep understanding of <strong>software engineering</strong>. I also benefited from an international mobility program that enabled me to broaden my horizons and develop my skills in <strong>Machine Learning</strong> and <strong>Big-Data</strong>.
                <br><br>
                Having had the privilege of receiving a quality education myself, I understand the importance of training future generations of learners.
            <strong>Since September 2023, I have been teaching</strong> the "Intégration et performance des Systèmes d'Information" course at the university. </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        <div class="h-screen -mt-12 pt-12">
            <div id="studies-part">
                <SubTitle title="Field of Studies and Expertises ?" />
                <div class="bordure"></div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-is-2">
                    <div>
                        <ul class="max-w-md space-y-1 list-disc list-inside dark:text-gray-400">
                            <li>Software engineering</li>
                            <li>Enterprise Application Architecture</li>
                            <li>Software testing</li>
                            <li>Model-driven engineering</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <ul class="max-w-md space-y-1 list-disc list-inside dark:text-gray-400">
                            <li>Middleware</li>
                            <li>Concurrent system</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <ul class="max-w-md space-y-1 list-disc list-inside dark:text-gray-400">
                            <li>Machine Learning</li>
                            <li>BigData</li>
                            <li>Operations research</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div id="skills-part">
                <div class="mt-12">
                    <SubTitle title="Technical skills" />
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-is-2">
                        <div>
                            <ul class="max-w-md space-y-1 list-disc list-inside dark:text-gray-400">
                                <li>Java, JEE, Spring</li>
                                <li>Maven</li>
                                <li>UML, BPMN</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="text-network" class="relative h-80">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 items-center justify-center mt-4 px-8 gap-x-20 max-w-72 md:max-w-screen-lg mx-auto text-center">
                    <a href="/resources/cv-fr.pdf" class="font-black px-4 py-2 my-2 text-gray-800 uppercase bg-transparent border-2 border-gray-800 md:mt-16 dark:text-gray-800 dark:bg-white hover:dark:bg-gray-100 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-white text-md">
                        FR
                    </a>
                    <a href="/resources/cv-en.pdf" class="font-black px-4 py-2 my-2 text-gray-800 uppercase bg-transparent border-2 border-gray-800 md:mt-16 dark:text-gray-800 dark:bg-white hover:dark:bg-gray-100 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-white text-md">
                        EN
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adriencaubel" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 my-2 text-gray-800 uppercase bg-transparent border-2 border-gray-800 md:mt-16 dark:text-gray-800 dark:bg-white hover:dark:bg-gray-100 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-white text-md">
                        <i class="text-2xl fa fa-linkedin"></i>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/adrien1212" target="_blank" class="px-4 py-2 my-2 text-gray-800 uppercase bg-transparent border-2 border-gray-800 md:mt-16 dark:text-gray-800 dark:bg-white hover:dark:bg-gray-100 dark:text-white hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-white text-md">
                        <i class="text-2xl fa fa-github"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div> 
    </div>
</main>

<style>
#text-part {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInText 1.5s ease-in both;
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
}

@keyframes fadeInText {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate3d(0, -5%, 0);
    }

    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    }
}

#studies-part {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInStudies 1.25s ease-in both;
    animation-delay: 1s;
}

@keyframes fadeInStudies {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate3d(-2%, 0%, 0);
    }

    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    }
}

#skills-part {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInSkills 1.25s ease-in both;
    animation-delay: 1.8s;
}

@keyframes fadeInSkills {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate3d(-2%, 0%, 0);
    }

    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    }
}

#text-network {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInNetwork 1.25s ease-in both;
    animation-delay: 2.4s;
}

@keyframes fadeInNetwork {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translate3d(0%, -2%, 0);
    }

    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    }
}
</style>